I've recruited a high-level Iranian asset.

54
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:02,550
馬吉德·賈瓦迪
Majid Javadi.

55
00:02:02,550 --> 00:02:05,250
中央情報局恐怖爆炸事件的策劃者
The man who financed the bombing of the CIA.

56
00:02:05,250 --> 00:02:06,880
我們已經談過
We talked about this.

57
00:02:07,650 --> 00:02:10,540
