He didn't die in the explosion like they say.

73
00:02:43,330 --> 00:02:45,510
據我所知  他還在美國
As far as I know, he's still in this country.

74
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,360
什么地方
Where?

75
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,260
我不知道
I don't know.

76
