誰知道
Who does?

77
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:50,240
就是促成我們會面的人
The man that brought us together.

78
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:52,490
是你的律師  是本尼特嗎
Your lawyer? Bennett?

79
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,980
你怎么這么殷勤  我會多想的
What happened to you? I started to get worried.

80
00:03:34,980 --> 00:03:36,470
太久沒表現  都生疏了
I'm out of practice.

81
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:44,400
