I'd like to go back to that island on the Sulu Sea.

90
00:04:04,310 --> 00:04:06,660
你不必承諾任何事
You know, you don't have to promise anything.

91
00:04:06,670 --> 00:04:09,520
真的  我都明白
Really. I understand.

92
00:04:09,670 --> 00:04:11,320
有何不可呢
No, I don't see why not.

93
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,700
我們可以開開心心的
We might actually have fun.

94
00:04:14,340 --> 00:04:15,890
不過看目前情況
Well, the evidence does seem to indicate

95
00:04:15,890 --> 00:04:17,920
確實有實現的可能
