不過我今早得去白宮和麥克·希金斯見面
I got a meeting with Mike Higgins this morning at the white house.

101
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:45,030
-幾點  -九點半
- When? - 9:30.

102
00:04:46,710 --> 00:04:49,050
