Well, that gives us an hour and a half...

103
00:04:50,150 --> 00:04:51,390
一個半小時
by my count.

104
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,990
那當然
Yes, it does.

105
00:05:04,900 --> 00:05:06,360
