109
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:16,550
內勤  分析跨國事務
Intelligence-- office of transnational issues.

110
00:05:16,570 --> 00:05:18,720
他和利蘭·本尼特有什么關系
And what's his connection to Leland Bennett?

111
00:05:18,930 --> 00:05:21,000
他寫了很長的報告
He wrote a lengthy analysis

112
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,860
分析他們公司幕后的客戶
of the firm's hip-pocket clients.

113
00:05:22,860 --> 00:05:24,930
伊朗  敘利亞  阿塞拜疆的
Iran, Syria, Azerbaijan.

114
00:05:24,930 --> 00:05:26,560
不過是兩年前
