Yeah, which begs the question--

120
00:05:39,890 --> 00:05:43,570
能確定是那炸彈客挪了布洛迪的車嗎
are we even sure that the guy who made the bomb moved Brody's car?

121
00:05:44,020 --> 00:05:45,620
-看怎么講了  -怎么講
- Depends. - On what?

122
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:47,350
