has been turned inside-out and upside-down.

131
00:06:01,770 --> 00:06:05,270
是  但那場爆炸肯定是現場某人搞的
Yeah, well, someone who was at Langley that day did the bombing.

132
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:14,630
