Yeah.

134
00:06:20,490 --> 00:06:21,730
法拉去哪了
Where's Fara anyway?

135
00:06:21,730 --> 00:06:23,850
她一個多小時前就該過來的
She was supposed to be here over an hour ago.

136
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:25,170
