147
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:53,520
我根本不知曉有任何逮捕賈瓦迪上校的指令
I'm not aware of any standing order to arrest Colonel Javadi.

148
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:56,080
-那你羈押他沒有  -羈押了
- Did you have him in custody or not? - I did.

149
