Because I know the man.

160
00:08:13,350 --> 00:08:14,670
因為他知道游戲規則
Because he knows the game.

161
00:08:14,670 --> 00:08:16,760
這完全是臆斷
That is total speculation.

162
00:08:16,990 --> 00:08:18,010
他說得對
He's right.

163
00:08:18,530 --> 00:08:20,060
最近這個部門的工作
We haven't had a whole lot of success

164
00:08:20,060 --> 00:08:21,230
