166
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,320
最有價值的線人
in the history of the agency.

167
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:28,470
他指揮了總部爆炸案  并為其提供資金
He ordered and financed the attack on Langley.

168
00:08:28,470 --> 00:08:30,550
那再好不過了  沒人會懷疑他
All the better if he did. He's above suspicion.

