177
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:47,040
必須當場做出決定
The call had to be made in real time.

178
00:08:47,050 --> 00:08:49,820
他心知肚明  這就是鬼扯
That is horseshit, and he knows it.

179
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:54,710
