Sorry this is so last-minute.

475
00:24:35,180 --> 00:24:37,220
不  很高興見到你
No, no, it's great to see you.

476
00:24:37,820 --> 00:24:39,380
真是個驚喜
This is quite a surprise.

477
00:24:39,380 --> 00:24:40,840
上周我還在院里見到了麥琪
I saw Maggie at the hospital last week,

478
00:24:40,840 --> 00:24:42,280
