she didn't say a thing.

479
00:24:42,390 --> 00:24:43,700
她不知道
She doesn't know.

480
00:24:44,300 --> 00:24:45,560
這跟你為什么第13周
Does that have anything to do with

481
00:24:45,560 --> 00:24:48,960
