I didn't exactly plan this.

483
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:55,470
但你知道自己懷孕已經有一陣子了吧
But you've known for some time.

484
00:24:58,860 --> 00:24:59,980
用藥情況如何
What about medications?

485
