What are you currently taking?

486
00:25:01,620 --> 00:25:03,620
現在什么藥都沒吃
Uh, at the moment, nothing.

487
00:25:03,820 --> 00:25:05,050
明白了
I see.

488
00:25:06,060 --> 00:25:07,970
我在"那地方"的一個月內每天服用
I was on 1,800 milligrams of lithium

489
00:25:07,970 --> 00:25:09,650
1800毫克的鋰[起鎮定作用]
for about a month there.

490
00:25:10,120 --> 00:25:11,850
當時事情有點失控
Things were a little out of control.

491
00:25:11,850 --> 00:25:13,750
更早之前
And, uh, before that,

492
00:25:14,470 --> 00:25:16,140
我喝過很多酒
there was a lot of drinking.

493
00:25:16,780 --> 00:25:19,020
非常多
A... lot.

494
00:25:20,390 --> 00:25:21,600
在你知道自己懷孕之后嗎
After you knew?

495
00:25:24,150 --> 00:25:28,350
直說了吧  我壓根沒想過要養孩子
I haven't been painting a nursery, just put it that way.

496
