你缺鐵
You're iron deficient.

500
00:25:40,360 --> 00:25:41,210
這個我們可以補回來
We can fix that.

501
00:25:41,220 --> 00:25:43,380
但你的血壓非常高
But your blood pressure's very high.

502
00:25:44,980 --> 00:25:47,950
我的工作壓力非常大
I've been... really stressed at work.

503
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:49,940
你真的應該放松一下
Well, you really should be taking it easy.

504
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:52,760
是啊  我會試試看
Yeah, I'll try.

505
00:25:53,830 --> 00:25:55,580
